            <h2>Why Children Should Understand Digital Wallets</h2>
            
            <div class="kid-crypto-grid">
                <div class="kid-crypto-info">
                    <h3>Financial Literacy for the Digital Age</h3>
                    <p>Today's children are growing up in a world where digital currencies and blockchain technology are becoming increasingly important. Understanding these concepts early provides them with valuable skills for their future.</p>
                    
                    <ul class="benefit-list">
                        <li><strong>Early Financial Education:</strong> Digital wallets introduce children to concepts like saving, spending, and the value of money in an engaging way.</li>
                        <li><strong>Future-Ready Skills:</strong> As blockchain technology becomes more mainstream, familiarity with digital wallets prepares children for future opportunities.</li>
                        <li><strong>Responsibility and Ownership:</strong> Managing their own digital assets teaches children about responsibility and the consequences of their decisions.</li>
                        <li><strong>Privacy and Security Awareness:</strong> Learning about wallet security helps children understand the importance of protecting personal information online.</li>
                        <li><strong>STEM Education Enhancement:</strong> Blockchain technology incorporates mathematics, cryptography, and computer science concepts in practical applications.</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <p>At Whiz Kids Tutoring, we believe in preparing children not just for today's world, but for the technologies that will shape their future careers and lives.</p>
                </div>
                
